                                VPN > OpenVPN > Client Export
                                OPEN VPN CLIENTS e faça o dowload do most client
                                Botão direito no simbolo da ethernet
                                Import > Importar o arquivo .ovpn que foi baixado
                                Conectar
             
              

              Regra para pingar:

                        Firewall > Rules > OpenVPN
                        Add
                        Action: Pass
                        Interface: OpenVPN
                        Address Family: IPv4
                        Protocol: ICMP
                        Source: any
                        Destination: any
                        Save - Apply Changes

               Regra para acessar com ssh:

                        Firewall > Rules > OpenVPN
                        Add
                        Action: Pass
                        Interface: OpenVPN
                        Address Family: IPv4
                        Protocol: TCP
                        Source: any
                        Destination: any
                        Destination Port Range: SSH (22)
                        Save - Apply Changes


